{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8f31da86e5","title":"关于两条路线斗争的基本问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d3bd5fdf97","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"8f31da86e5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"877762393f","name":"两条路线斗争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoxuan-jinghuo","name":"毛泽东选集1-7（静火版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"静火","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/maoxuan-jinghuo.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoxuan-jinghuo":{"comments":[{"id":"69845f7173","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8f31da86e5","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"这是毛泽东同志为中共中央起草的党内指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"120ca88e32","type":"title","text":"关于两条路线斗争的基本问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8f31da86e5"},{"id":"8147adbe15","type":"paragraph","text":"我们党内两条路线斗争，基本问题是在无产阶级夺取政权之以后，即新民主主义革命胜利以后，中国究竟走资本主义道路，还是走社会主义道路的问题。资产阶级要走资本主义道路，这是很明显的。在我们共产党内部，我们要走社会主义道路；但有一部分人却认为中国是个很穷困的国家，中国资本主义发展水平很低，不能发展社会主义，必须在一段时间内走资产阶级道路，然后再走社会主义道路。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8f31da86e5"},{"id":"05d07ac1ae","type":"paragraph","text":"走什么道路问题，解放初期有这个问题，现在仍然有这个问题。苏联搞了五十多年，仍是这个问题。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8f31da86e5"}],"page":{"id":"8853edbb98","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8f31da86e5","start":1599,"end":1599}}}},"__N_SSG":true}